qText.desc: The text version of the value, if available.

qRow.desc:
Row index in the data matrix.
The indexing starts from 0.

qNodeNr.desc: A generated number applicable to this page only. Used so that children can easily identify who their parents are.

qParentNode.desc: The qNodeNr of this node's parent for the current page.

values.V: NX_DIM_CELL_VALUE. Applies to values in the data matrix.
values.E: NX_DIM_CELL_EMPTY. Applies to empty cells in the top and left dimensions.
values.G: NX_DIM_CELL_GENERATED. Applies to generated nodes that are inserted into the returned tree when there is no actual value (qAllValues in NxPageTreeNode set to true).
values.N: NX_DIM_CELL_NORMAL. Applies to left and top dimensions cells.
values.T: NX_DIM_CELL_TOTAL. Applies to cells marked with Total.
values.U: NX_DIM_CELL_NULL. Applies to Null values in the data matrix.

qNodes.desc: The children of this node in the tree structure.
